---
title: Sri Lankan Chicken & Roast Veggie Curry  with Garlic Rice, Roasted Cashews & Coriander
description: This dish comes with a big juicy warning - it’s too delicious to refuse. Be lured to the table when you get
a good wiff of the Sri Lankan spiced veggies and chicken tossed in a tomato-based creamy curry.
